annotationA: Dolichyl-diphosphooligosaccharide--protein glycosyltransferase 48 kDa subunit; Essential subunit of the N-oligosaccharyl transferase (OST) complex which catalyzes the transfer of a high mannose oligosaccharide from a lipid-linked oligosaccharide donor to an asparagine residue within an Asn-X-Ser/Thr consensus motif in nascent polypeptide chains
annotationB: Glucosidase 1, isoform B; Mannosyl-oligosaccharide glucosidase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: oligosaccharide metabolic process
